    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "UNITED AIRLINES CARGO\nEffective October 31, 1982\nUnited's Freighter schedule is\nlooking' good—with some great\nnew advantages for shippers:\nOur Chicago hub:\n• More available space\n• 12 departures —all prime time\nCleveland and Detroit:\n• More and better service to West Coast markets\n• Earlier arrival in Los Angeles\nDenver, Seattle, Portland:\n• Prime-time connections for East Coast cities via\nChicago\nSan Francisco and Los Angeles: the same great\nnonstop service to New York!\nand we're\nsupporting these improvements with even greater\nschedule reliability."
